    "Name": "Fire Wasp IIC 1",
    "Details": "The Fire Wasp IIC is Clan Hell's Horses' full reimagining of the lineage, scaling up to 60 tons while retaining the speed and jump capability that defines the chassis. MASC pushes it to 129 kph in bursts while six jump jets provide outstanding repositioning. Four ER Flamers make heat management a serious concern for anything they touch, and twin Medium Pulse Lasers with a Streak SRM 6 deliver reliable direct damage. Every Clan ran these by the Jihad era.\n\n<b><color=#e62e00>Quirk: Agile</color></b>\n\n<b><color=#e62e00>Drop Cost Multiplier: 1.14</color></b>",
